83
00:05:59,600 --> 00:06:00,720
Claro que sí.

84
00:06:02,800 --> 00:06:04,960
Puedes saludarme cada vez que me veas.

85
00:06:06,440 --> 00:06:07,760
O...

86
00:06:10,120 --> 00:06:11,640
